Paper: hep-th/0010077

Date: 2000-10-11

Title: Sigma Model Corrections to the Confining Background

Authors: Enrique Alvarez, Manuel Donaire and Lorenzo Hernandez

Comments: LaTeX,12 pages

Journal-ref: JHEP 0011 (2000) 003

Sigma model ($\alpha^{\prime}$) corrections to the confining stringbackground are obtained. The main result is that the Poincar\'e invariantansatz is maintained. Physical conditions for the dissapearance of the nakedsingularity are discussed.